org.matsim.contrib.locationchoice.population

Class LCPlan

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.matsim.contrib.locationchoice.population.LCPlan
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Customizable, BasicPlan, Plan, MatsimExtensionPoint, MatsimPopulationObject, Attributable

    public class LCPlan
extends Object
implements Plan
    Optimized data structure used in the location choice contribution. There, a huge amount of plans are created and evaluated, which is time consuming and increases the workload for the garbage collector. This class uses an optimized data structure designed especially for that application. There is no guarantee that it can be utilized for other applications!
    Author:
    cdobler
